21/09/2010
SARAJEVO, Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) -- Police arrested two people Monday (September 20th) suspected of committing war crimes against Serbian civilians and prisoners of war. Galib. H, 63, was detained in Brcko while Nijaz H, 50, was arrested in Sarajevo. The two were allegedly involved in crimes committed near Brcko, in September 1992. (RTRS, Tanjug, B92 - 20/09/10)
